Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:02.78,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,这集绝对是福利回
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对是福利回啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:07.27,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,我是不是给自己立了flag
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:11.32,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\fs16\alpha&H66&\an7\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0075EA&}ACG12调查小队【沉默似金_】抄自【F宅字幕组】\N仅供学习交流，禁止用于任何商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:11.32,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an2}{\1c&HA86C6F&}Re{\1c&HA9AB4B&}:{\1c&H7D60CC&}小{\1c&H4396E0&}剧场 {\1c&H000000&}其九
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:16.11,Petit,Title,0,0,0,,{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}小{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}剧场{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HC4C700&\b1\bord6}⑨{\bord2}{\1c&HBB878E&\3c&HFFFFFF&}西{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}瓜{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HB8B80F&}攻略战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:14.46,Default,Crusch,0,0,0,,你这样盯着我看 是有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:17.82,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,啊不 我只是在想 库珥修的泳装真帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:19.53,Default,Crusch,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:22.19,Default,Crusch,0,0,0,,虽然这形容并不适用于泳装打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:24.29,Default,Crusch,0,0,0,,但直率又顺耳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.53,0:00:27.85,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,直率又爱说正是昴君的魅力所在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:28.73,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:29.69,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,雷姆的泳装打扮也是破坏力拔群
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:33.22,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,真是鬼上身了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:34.49,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么想娶回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:39.76,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,虽然很可爱 但我没说到那份上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:44.48,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,但如果不分对象地说出这种话会招致误会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.91,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,请务必将对象只限于艾米莉娅大人和雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:49.00,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,真是顺势而为呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:51.08,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:53.98,Default,Crusch,0,0,0,,我在想卿们的感情真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:55.98,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,是的 感情非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:59.12,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,如此坦然地被这么说 就算是事实我也会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:01.47,Default,Crusch,0,0,0,,不过卿也是跟他们志气相投的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:02.51,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,蛤！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么一说好像真的是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:07.73,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,比起这些 难得的机会 不来玩切西瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:10.26,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,为了能玩个尽兴我带了很多西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:12.80,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,雷姆小姐一如既往地值得信赖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:16.70,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,库珥修 往右往右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:19.81,Default,Crusch,0,0,0,,哼 这种谎话是骗不到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:23.14,Default,Crusch,0,0,0,,卿难道忘记了我的力量了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:25.60,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,难道在这个世界也有风之加护
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:29.38,Default,Crusch,0,0,0,,我就算被蒙着眼也能有点明白西瓜的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:30.77,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,和加护没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:39.03,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,等等你把第一次的当做没发生了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:41.91,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,好厉害 但雷姆不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:46.40,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,那个 雷姆小姐 雷姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:47.82,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,是的 昴君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:49.82,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,您手上拿的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:51.26,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,用来切西瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:52.54,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,切西瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:54.71,Default,Rem,0,0,0,,是的 用来切西瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.22,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,砸了个稀巴烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:00.72,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,炸了个稀巴烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.98,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,你别突然出现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:06.10,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,变成这样就没法卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.54,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,话说我还在想切好的西瓜去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是被你卖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:12.42,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,你在说啥啊 真是诬陷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:16.13,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,美女切开的西瓜只要100円什么的我才没干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:19.25,Default,Crusch,0,0,0,,从卿的话中看到谎言的风了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:23.23,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,不愧是有看破谎言能力的贤才呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.45,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,风之加护 不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:30.46,SignA,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs10\bord5\pos(442,223)\an6\1c&H777777&\3c&H403D88&}美女切开的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:30.46,SignA,Subaru,0,0,0,,{\fs13\bord2\pos(442,240)\an4\1c&H267297&\3c&H000000&}西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:30.46,SignA,Subaru,0,0,0,,{\fs11\bord2\pos(467,255)\an4\1c&H506A53&\3c&H999999&}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:29.41,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,这和加护没关系 是百分之百会暴露的谎言吧
